title: Disney Theme Song Collection
description:
Thanks for seeding my first torrent ;)


This is a compilation of the most memorable main themes from Disney
animated features performed by their original artists (the exception
being track one), spanning from The Little Mermaid to Bolt. This
revised torrent contains the corrected track no 09 and a couple more
songs from other Disney theatrical features.
Included is some original artwork with a track listing of how all of 
the songs would work as a 3 CD set. ENJOY & SEED!


All tracks are of excellent quality, mainly 192 kbps
